Package org.oa4mp.server.loader.qdl.claims

Interface CSConstants

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ClaimSourceConfigConverter, ClaimsSourceGetter, ConfigtoCS, CreateSourceConfig, NewTemplate
    public interface CSConstants
    The constants for creating claim sources so that they are centralized. These are the property names that appear in QDL configuration objects.

    Created by Jeff Gaynor
